               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Gawhar-i murād by ʿAbd al-Razzāq ibn ʿAlī ibn al-Ḥusayn al-Lāhijī</summary>
                  <msItem class="https://lccn.loc.gov/sh2010113603 https://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008112367" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1098-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Compendium of Twelver Shi'ism by 
                <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656389.0x000001 viaf_16145304708378611094" role="aut">ʿAbd al-Razzāq ibn ʿAlī ibn al-Ḥusayn al-Lāhijī</persName>, dedicated to 
                <persName key="viaf_268954445" role="dte">Shāh ʿAbbās II Ṣafavī</persName>(r. 1052-1077/1642-1667).
                        </p>
                        <p>The work comprises a muqaddimah, three maqālah, concluding with a khātimah.</p>
                        <p>Dated colophon, damaged (f. 136v): written in haste, Thursday, 6 [Rama]z̤ān 1122/9 October 1710.</p>
                        <p>Rounded naskh.</p>
                        <p>Annotations and correction in margins; collation marks.</p>
                        <p>Diagrams of the irregular orbit of the moon around the earth (f. 17v); the latitudinal division of the earth into iqlīm or climes (f. 19r); orbits and divisions of the heavens (ff. 76v-77v).</p>
                        <p>Stamped foliation.</p>
                        <p>Multiple phases of Persian foliation added on upper extended margins and lower edge.</p>
                        <p>Later dark brown, blind tooled leather covers lacking inner boards.</p>
                        <p>Folios loose and disarranged, with several lacunae; severely affected by wormholes, stains, tears, creases, and aggressive copping; later repairs.</p>
                     </note>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_20125">Gawhar-i murād</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_20125">گوهر مراد</title>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_16145304708378611094">ʿAbd al-Razzāq ibn ʿAlī ibn al-Ḥusayn al-Lāhijī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_16145304708378611094">عبد الرزاق ابن علي ابن الحسين اللاهجي</persName>
                     </author>
